# Math Module - Allocation-Free Integer Math for Baremetal
#
# Provides basic integer math utilities suitable for bare-metal targets.
# No heap allocation. All functions operate on stack values only.
#
# Public API:
#   - use std.math.{bm_abs, bm_min, bm_max, bm_clamp}
#   - use std.math.{bm_pow, bm_isqrt}
#   - use std.math.{bm_gcd, bm_lcm}

# All functions exported from mod.spl are automatically available.
